{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20260429/photo/bkn-20260429154155492-0429_00992_001_01p.jpg?20260429154520\" alt=\"\"><p>他信獲准假釋。（Getty Images圖片）</p><p>泰國司法部假釋委員會周三（29日）決定，允許前總理他信於5月11日假釋出獄，毋須佩戴電子監控手環。</p><p>上一則 下一則</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T07:53:05.121566+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":81,"images":1,"source":"東網 國際","fallback":"none"}}